(14)Department of Neuroscience, Psychiatry, Uppsala University, Uppsala, Sweden.
(15)Department of Anaesthesiology and Intensive Care, and Department of Clinical 
and Experimental Medicine, Linköping University, Linköping, Sweden.
(16)Department of Health and Caring Sciences, Faculty of Health and Social 
Sciences, Western Norway University of Applied Sciences, Bergen, Norway.
(17)Department of Plastic, Hand and Reconstructive Surgery, National Burn 
