Factors associated with a risk of prosthetic knee buckling during walking in 
unilateral transfemoral amputees.

Hisano G(1), Hashizume S(2), Kobayashi Y(3), Murai A(3), Kobayashi T(4), 
Nakashima M(2), Hobara H(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Systems and Control Engineering, Tokyo Institute of Technology, 
